            ],
            "stanza_text": "D'où venez-vous ? Du Lignon ?\nDis-je à la jeune mortelle.\nNon, je sors de chez Bignon,\nMonsieur, me répondit-elle."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Quel compère Guilleri",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Vous a si bien chiffonnée ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Dis-je. C'est le Sillery,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Dit cette désordonnée.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quel compère Guilleri\nVous a si bien chiffonnée ?\nDis-je. C'est le Sillery,\nDit cette désordonnée."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ses yeux riants, dans le soir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Faisaient l'effet d'un prodige,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Tout embrasés d'un feu noir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Chère madame, lui dis-je,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ses yeux riants, dans le soir\nFaisaient l'effet d'un prodige,\nTout embrasés d'un feu noir.\nChère madame, lui dis-je,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Que de Jeux et que de Ris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Nichent sous votre dentelle !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ces articles de Paris ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Oui, je les tiens, me dit-elle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que de Jeux et que de Ris\nNichent sous votre dentelle !\nCes articles de Paris ?\nOui, je les tiens, me dit-elle,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Pour que mon cœur, sans émoi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Du destin amer se rie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et je m'en vais devant moi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Avec cette mercerie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour que mon cœur, sans émoi,\nDu destin amer se rie,\nEt je m'en vais devant moi\nAvec cette mercerie."
